outputs.prompt: List 3 movies about sci-fi in the genre of fiction.
List 3 movies about sci-fi in the genre of fiction.

outputs.report: These three films explore the complex relationship between humans and artificial intelligence. In 'Ex Machina,' a programmer interacts with a humanoid AI, questioning consciousness and morality. 'I Am Mother' features a girl raised by a robot in a post-extinction world, who challenges her understanding of trust and the outside world when a human arrives. 'Mother/Android' follows a pregnant woman and her boyfriend navigating a post-apocalyptic landscape controlled by hostile androids, highlighting themes of survival and human resilience.
